    <briefdescription>
<para>Represents the parsed contents of a password file. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Splits the file into a password line, named key/value fields, and remaining data. Use <ref refid="class_file_content_1af8c5c3b19e2f1244c5e83aa40521ebde" kindref="member">FileContent::parse</ref> to construct an instance. </para>
